<wpforewd>
<para0><?Pub Dtl><title> PURPOSE</title>
<para>The individual WORK PACK forewords contain information pertaining
to that WORK PACK only. <xref xrefid="t004-00-1"></para>
</para0>
<para0 applicref="a"><?Pub Dtl><title> SCOPE</title>
<para>If any information normally contained in a Foreword pertains
to this WORK PACK only list it in the appropriate primary sidehead.
Examples list below:<randlist>
<item>Abbreviation for this WORK PACK.</item>
<item>Applicability/Effectivity for this WORK PACK</item>
<item>Symbols used in this WORK PACK.</item>
</randlist></para>
